posts.title: LUCKY PATCHER: Get Started?
posts.description: Lucky Patcher is an incredible and useful tool that gives you full control over the permissions you give to the apps installed on your device. You can remove excessive advertising, create backups. change the permissions of other apps and much more...
posts.written:
Lucky Patcher is an incredible and useful tool that gives you full control over the permissions you give to the apps installed on your device.

You can remove excessive advertising, create backups. change the permissions of other apps and much more.

But you do need a rooted device in order to enjoy these features.

When you open for the first time Lucky Patcher App you will find a list of all the apps installed on your android device. All you have to do is just tap one of them to see the available options:
- View the app's information.
- Uninstall it.
- Delete additional data.
- Access other special tools
